dialogueTree.title: Sunday Friend: ""First responsabilité, then stabili..."
dialogueTree.polish: „Najpierw responsabilité, później stabilité i w końcu prospérité!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Спачатку responsabilité, потым stabilité і нарэшце prospérité!»

dialogueTree.title: Sunday Friend: ""The sea air is so invigorating, do..."
dialogueTree.english: "The sea air is so invigorating, don't you agree?"

dialogueTree.title: Sunday Friend: ""Lots of opportunities for revitali..."
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Я бачу тут шмат магчымасцяў для рэвіталізацыі».

dialogueTree.title: Sunday Friend: ""This whole area is a strong candid..."
dialogueTree.english: "This whole area is a strong candidate for a micro-loan."
dialogueTree.polish: „Cały ten obszar jest ma duże szanse na mikropożyczkę”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Увесь гэты рэгіён мае вялікія шанцы на мікракрэдыт».

dialogueTree.title: Sunday Friend: ""Even high-ranking bureaucrats are..."
dialogueTree.english: "Even high-ranking bureaucrats are entitled to a holiday."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nawet wysoko postawieni biurokraci mają prawo do urlopu”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Нават высокапастаўленыя бюракратары маюць права на адпачынак».
